<h1>Your Order is Ready for Collection - #<%= @order.prefix_id %></h1>

<p>Hi <%= @customer.name %>,</p>

<p>Good news! Your order is now ready for collection at the shop.</p>

<h3>Order Summary</h3>
<ul>
  <% @order.order_items.each do |item| %>
    <li><%= item.inventory_item.display_name %> x <%= item.quantity %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Total: <%= @order.total_amount.format %></p>

<p>Payment is required on collection. We look forward to seeing you!</p>